    "title": "SeaKing Bait Board H10 (830mm x 400mm)",
    "body_html": "<p><strong>SeaKing SK-H10 Premium Fiberglass Bait Board [white]</strong></p>\n<p>Handcrafted from full composite materials. The<span> </span><strong>SeaKing SK-H10</strong><span> </span>is built to perform and endure. Featuring a<span> </span><strong>UV-resistant PE plastic cutting board</strong><span> </span>a<span> </span><strong>large integrated sink<span> </span></strong>and<strong><span> </span>drain</strong>, with optional rod holders and cup holders for added versatility. A spacious rear<span> </span><strong>knife tray</strong><span> </span>keeps tools within easy reach.</p>",
